Detailed Description

template<class T>
class Util::Queue< T >

Double linked list (thread unsafe)

The queue descriptor is linked to the first and the last elements. We can define a queue of Queable cells if X derived from Queable<X>: 

    Queue<X> Q_of_X;
Warning:
In deletion, queue must be empty. In insertion, cell must be defined (not 0).
See also:
List, StackList
